; fpto{u/s}i (fdiv ({u/s}itofp X), C) -> {u/s}div X, C
; Unsigned: sound when C >= 1 and N <= p.
; Signed: sound when C not in {0, -1} and N - 1 <= p.
; (N = integer width, p = FP mantissa width.)

